string.name: provisional
string.comment:
provisional
This marker indicates a rating is provisional. This happens when the rating deviation is too high, and the player needs more games (typically) so we can be more sure on the rating.

resources.string: Níor imríodh go leor cluichí rátáilte chun rátáil iontaofa a bhunú.
Ciallaíonn luach níos ísle go bhfuil an rátáil níos cobhsaí. Os cionn %s, meastar go bhfuil an rátáil sealadach.
